description:
Stuck with Hackett - Laundromat of the Gods
 
Original Air Date: Aug 25, 2011
Runtime: 21 minutes
Video: XviD
Audio: MP3
 
Hackett aims to build a washer and dryer using old car parts found in the junkyard which requires him not only to build a welder but also to rethink the spin cycle and use exhaust fumes to create heat in order to dry the washed clothes.
